  "instructions": [
    "Heat the sesame oil in a donabe over medium heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the sliced zucchini and grated carrots, cooking for 3-4 minutes until they start to soften.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the rose water, ferment-jang, and soy sauce, then pour the mixture over the vegetables.",
    "Stir in the chopped green onions, toasted sesame seeds, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 10 minutes until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Serve the namul hot, garnished with additional green onions and sesame seeds if desired.",
    "Let it cool slightly before serving to allow the flavors to meld together."
  ],
